<br>
Bard Epic Checklist<br>
Contributed by Baerd Brightsong<br>
Interactive version coming soon! Bard Epic Checklist <br>
<br>
Top Half of Page 24 <br>
 Talk to Konia Swiftfoot, receive a torch <br>
 Give the torch to Fajio Knejo, receive torch <br>
 Give the torch to Andad Filla, receive torch <br>
 Give the torch to Misty Tekchita, receive ring <br>
 Give the ring to Konia Swiftfoot, receive top of page 24 <br>
<br>
Bottom Half of Page 24 <br>
 Ask Braenar Swiftsong, &quot;what doll,&quot; receive invoice <br>
 Take the invoice to Marfen Birkdipple, receive a &quot;doll&quot; <br>
 Give the doll to Serra, receive a note <br>
 Give the note to Braenar, receive a note <br>
 Give the note to Maligar <br>
<br>
Kill Maligar's Enraged Doppleganger, loot his head <br>
 Give the head Braenar, recieve Mahlin's Bongo's <br>
 Give the Bongo's to Konia Swiftfoot, receive the bottom  of Page 24. <br>
<br>
Page 25 <br>
 Kill Blackwing in Rathe Mountains, loot drake guts <br>
 Kill Nezekezena or Phurzicon in Burning Woods, loot wurm guts <br>
 Kill Eldrig the Old in Skyfire, loot chromodrac guts <br>
 Give all the guts to Kelkim Menkia, receive Page 25 <br>
<br>
Forpar's Lute <br>
 Mystical Lute Head <br>
 Kill Quag Maeslstrom, loot Alluring Horn. <br>
 Give Alluring Horn to Vedico Windwhisper, receive a note <br>
 Give note to Forpar, receive a note and list <br>
 Kill Phinigel, loot backbone <br>
 Kill an Amygdalan in Plane of Fear, loot Amygdalan Tendril <br>
 Kill Drolvarg Warlord, loot skull <br>
 Give note, backbone, tendril and skull to Forpar, receive Mystical Lute Head <br>
<br>
Mystical Lute Body <br>
 Kill a red dragon (Nagafen, Ragefire, Talendor, Nortlav Scalekeeper), loot red dragon scale <br>
 Kill a white dragon (Vox, Gorenaire), loot white dragon scale <br>
 Give the one metal bit (smithed), red scale and white scale to Forpar, receive Body of the Lute <br>
<br>
Strings for the Lute <br>
 Kill Trakanon, loot Trakanon gut strings <br>
<br>
Mystical Lute <br>
 Give Mystical Lute Head, Body of the Lute and Trakanon guts to Forpar, receive the Mystical Lute<br>
<br>
 <br>
Singing Short Sword! <br>
 Give Page 24 top, page 24 bottom, page 25 and Forpar's Lute to Baldric Slezaf, receive Singing Short Sword <br>
